<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 20:08:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列博物馆为伊朗袭击做好准备，马格利特和伦勃朗的杰作得到庇护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/magritte-rembrandt-masterpieces-take-shelter-as-israel-museum-braces-for-iranian-attack/00000191-47ce-d0da-afb1-57dfb0d00000</link><description>正如加沙战争初期所做的那样，耶路撒冷机构将其一些“最重要”的作品放置在受保护的空间中。特拉维夫艺术博物馆也采取了类似措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 19:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/magritte-rembrandt-masterpieces-take-shelter-as-israel-museum-braces-for-iranian-attack/00000191-47ce-d0da-afb1-57dfb0d00000</guid></item><item><title>美国主要学术联盟撤回抵制以色列大学的反对意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/major-u-s-academic-union-withdraws-opposition-to-boycotting-israeli-universities/00000191-479d-d732-adf5-c7bdc9590000</link><description>虽然美国大学教授协会的声明没有具体提及以色列，但加沙战争很可能是其在近二十年后重新审视其政策的原因。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 17:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/major-u-s-academic-union-withdraws-opposition-to-boycotting-israeli-universities/00000191-479d-d732-adf5-c7bdc9590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 311 天：据报道真主党撤离贝鲁特总部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-311-hezbollah-reportedly-evacuates-beirut-headquarters/00000191-474c-d1cf-a5dd-cf7c0ab20000</link><description>伊朗外长表示，伊朗有权对以色列采取“适当和威慑性反应”，以确保地区稳定 ■ 法国、德国、英国呼吁伊朗及其盟友不要发动可能危及加沙停战谈判的袭击 ■ 以色列国防部长致电内塔尼亚胡“全面胜利”口号“无稽之谈” ■ 福克斯新闻报道伊朗可能在 24 小时内袭击以色列 ■ 战争已经过去 311 天了，您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-311-hezbollah-reportedly-evacuates-beirut-headquarters/00000191-474c-d1cf-a5dd-cf7c0ab20000</guid></item><item><title>为什么 AIPAC 没有公开试图推翻伊尔汗·奥马尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-12/ty-article/.highlight/why-aipac-hasnt-publicly-tried-to-unseat-ilhan-omar/00000191-472b-db9a-a197-d7ef45540000</link><description>奥马尔与众议员拉希达·特莱布和亚历山大·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯一样，仍然受到选民的欢迎，并且没有选举上的弱点，而正是这些弱点使美国公共事务委员会能够帮助纽约的鲍曼和密苏里州的布什下台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-12/ty-article/.highlight/why-aipac-hasnt-publicly-tried-to-unseat-ilhan-omar/00000191-472b-db9a-a197-d7ef45540000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在驳回有关加沙战争“全面胜利”的言论后猛烈抨击国防部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-blasts-defense-minister-after-he-dismisses-talk-of-total-victory-in-gaza-war/00000191-4701-d7bb-a1df-ef6bd40a0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特对议会委员会表示，“我听到英雄们敲响了战争的鼓声，‘全面胜利’和胡言乱语”，促使总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡指责他采取了“反以色列的叙述”</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 15:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-blasts-defense-minister-after-he-dismisses-talk-of-total-victory-in-gaza-war/00000191-4701-d7bb-a1df-ef6bd40a0000</guid></item><item><title>汉莎航空和瑞士航空将暂停飞往以色列的航班至少延长至 8 月 21 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/lufthansa-and-swiss-extend-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-at-least-august-21/00000191-46e7-d7bb-a1df-efef150e0000</link><description>汉莎航空将延长飞往多个中东目的地的航班暂停时间，包括特拉维夫、贝鲁特、安曼和伊拉克埃尔比勒</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:32:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/lufthansa-and-swiss-extend-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-at-least-august-21/00000191-46e7-d7bb-a1df-efef150e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队拘留两名在约旦河西岸前哨袭击阿拉伯裔以色列妇女的嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-detain-two-suspects-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-at-west-bank-outpost/00000191-46c5-d7bb-a1df-efefe3f20000</link><description>《Shin Bet》称，两名被捕者涉嫌投掷石块、持武器威胁以及纵火焚烧女子汽车，将于明天举行听证会以延长拘留期限</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:25:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-detain-two-suspects-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-at-west-bank-outpost/00000191-46c5-d7bb-a1df-efefe3f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全官员警告极右翼活动分子可能在重新安置集会上闯入加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</link><description>这次祈祷集会是由定居者团体在犹太斋戒日 Tisha B&amp;#39;Av 之前组织的，预计将吸引数百人参加，其中包括以色列右翼议员。一位安全消息人士称，人们担心警察中的“本格维尔精神”可能会让军队独自面对数百名暴徒</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</guid></item><item><title>消息来源：哈马斯拒绝新提议并不意味着与以色列的谈判破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁调解人提出一项计划，从四月份开始实施拜登大纲，而不是提出任何关于人质/停火协议的新提议，这主要被视为一种战术举措，旨在在与以色列恢复谈判之前施加压力。至来源</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</guid></item><item><title>值得吗？关于以色列袭击中东的十大紧迫问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:43:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</guid></item><item><title>在最初的失败之后，以色列军队正在研究挽救极端正统派男子征召动力的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</link><description>以色列国防军人力局正在考虑让极端正统派男子到其常规入伍中心以外的地点报到，以减少他们遇到示威者的机会，并将征召日期延长一段时间</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军将军转为政治家的亚伊尔·戈兰：“不确定”以色列是否是一个民主国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</link><description>以色列新成立的中左翼政党民主党党魁亚伊尔·戈兰在接受《卫报》采访时表示支持两国解决方案，但强调这一过程可能需要数年时间。 “现在，我们是一个饱受创伤的国家。人们失去了安全感”</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</link><description>以色列国防军确认这名士兵是 19 岁的中士。 Omer Ginzburg，一名来自以色列北部的 19 岁伞兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：伊朗、真主党威胁下没有新的紧急措施；白宫预计以色列可能遭受“重大”袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article-live/idf-releases-name-of-combat-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-fighting/00000191-4452-d122-a7f5-ff77ca190000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道：西岸袭击事件中的枪手在11月人质协议中被公布 ■ 以色列国防军表示正在审查哈马斯关于一名以色列人质被绑架者枪杀的说法 ■ 西方领导人在声明中支持“以色列防御伊朗侵略” ■ 美国主要学术联盟撤回反对意见抵制以色列大学 ■ 约250名以色列人参加加沙边境的右翼祈祷集会，呼吁重新安置</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article-live/idf-releases-name-of-combat-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-fighting/00000191-4452-d122-a7f5-ff77ca190000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府在战争中推进司法政变，几乎没有反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-plows-ahead-with-judicial-coup-amid-war-and-with-little-opposition/00000191-42d7-dcc2-a9d1-4edf74230000</link><description>在基本不感兴趣的媒体、缺乏灵感的反对派和厌倦战争的公众的眼皮底下，内塔尼亚胡和他的走狗正忙着通过诋毁以色列的看门人来迎合他们的支持者</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-plows-ahead-with-judicial-coup-amid-war-and-with-little-opposition/00000191-42d7-dcc2-a9d1-4edf74230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁秘书告诉AG：你们的工作程序有缺陷，而不是内塔尼亚胡的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</link><description>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡，他的内阁工作程序存在缺陷，损害了公共利益——对国家安全造成严重影响——之后，内阁秘书指控总检察长超越了她的职权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长敦促政府恢复司法改革</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</link><description>在几位联盟议员呼吁罢免总检察长后，以色列司法部长亚里夫·莱文敦促他们与他一起努力重启司法改革，特别是通过一项法律，让政府对法官的选择有更多的控制权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:51:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡还是人质？美国犹太人是时候做出选择了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</link><description>每个关心以色列和人质的人都必须做出决定，他们是与被哈马斯扣押的人质家属站在一起，还是与失败的政客站在一起，我们永远不应该忘记，在这场暴行发生时，他们仍在掌权。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸驾车枪击事件中丧生，一人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</link><description>以色列军方认为，袭击者在西岸北部的90号公路上向一辆车开枪，随后继续行驶，并向第二辆车开枪。救援部门宣布一名受害者当场死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 310 天：据报道，官员要求真主党推迟对以色列袭击的答复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</link><description>以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列有迹象表明哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔希望达成停火/释放人质协议，并补充说“问题是内塔尼亚胡是否愿意” ■ 以色列男子在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 以色列政府采纳阻止协议访问真主党附属新闻频道 Al-Mayadeen ■ 这是战争 310 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</guid></item></channel></rss>